[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0305","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0305.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0362","title":"SuSE Linux cdwtools 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux cdwtools 093 及更早版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过向 cdwtools 程序提交特制的输入触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SuSE Linux 6.1/6.2 等发行版本，由于 cwdtools 以 setuid 权限运行，攻击者无需认证即可在本地利用此漏洞实现权限提升。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0362"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-10-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:33.543","remediation":"升级 cdwtools 至 093 以上版本，或从 SuSE 官方获取安全补丁。如无法升级，可移除 cwdtools 相关二进制文件的 setuid 权限位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/cwdtools），限制本地普通用户执行提权操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/suse_security_announce_25.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/738","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19565","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0362.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0362","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0362.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0362.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g52w-p8hr-3x85/GHSA-g52w-p8hr-3x85.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0362.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0305.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0888","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0888.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0327","title":"Microsoft Virtual Machine 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Virtual Machine（Microsoft VM）存在 Java 沙箱逃逸漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造包含非法类型转换操作（Illegal Cast Operation）的恶意 Java Applet，诱使用户访问后触发该漏洞，从而突破 Java 安全沙箱限制并在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft VM 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.6，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0327"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:29.123","remediation":"Microsoft Java Virtual Machine（Microsoft VM）已于 2007 年停止支持，建议立即卸载 Microsoft VM 并迁移至受支持的 Java 运行时环境（如 Oracle Java 或 OpenJDK）。在 Internet Explorer 中禁用 Java 小程序执行：工具 → Internet 选项 → 安全 → 自定义级别 → 禁用\"Java 小程序脚本\"。如无法立即卸载，将 Microsoft VM 升级至 Build 2442（2000 系列）或 Build 3188（3000 系列）以上版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93993545118416&w=2","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-045","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0327.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0327","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0327.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0327.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h9m3-4hrh-g7hx/GHSA-h9m3-4hrh-g7hx.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0327.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/839e2559933f5ff6cd50b4768fd382827d790668/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0888.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0039","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0039.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0047","title":"Yahoo Pager/Messenger 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Yahoo Pager（后更名为 Yahoo Messenger）客户端存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，当其解析接收到的即时消息中嵌入的超长 URL 时，因未对 URL 长度进行边界校验，导致缓冲区被溢出覆盖。未经身份认证的远程攻击者只需向目标用户发送一条包含超长 URL 的恶意消息，即可触发该漏洞造成客户端崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响当时使用 Yahoo Pager/Messenger 客户端的 Windows 用户，攻击条件为攻击者能够与受害用户建立聊天会话并发送消息，利用方式简单，无需本地访问权限或用户交互之外的操作，但仅造成拒绝服务而非代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0047"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:53.510","remediation":"建议立即升级 Yahoo Pager/Messenger 至 Yahoo 官方发布的安全补丁版本，或更换为最新版 Yahoo Messenger 客户端以修复缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙或网关层面过滤来自不可信来源的长 URL 消息作为临时缓解措施，或暂停使用 Yahoo Pager/Messenger 客户端，迁移至其他即时通讯工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0047","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0047.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0047.json","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/1f56e0f4599c42d2608c9795e223f08c91354b9f/2000/C