s Server 2012 R2 或更高版本，并启用注册表项 `HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\Tcpip\\Parameters\\SynAttackProtect` 为 1 以增强 SYN 洪水防护作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/604","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=4.1.19990824165629.00abcb40%40192.168.124.1","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-046","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0328.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0328","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0328.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0328.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pwww-664m-pfp9/GHSA-pwww-664m-pfp9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0328.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-656.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8ce591a6-a76c-4f3f-ba09-ca14e35b7720.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0329.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0271","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0271.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0325","title":"Microsoft JET 数据库引擎 VBA Shell 代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft JET 数据库引擎在处理特制数据库查询时存在 VBA Shell 漏洞，攻击者可通过构造恶意数据库查询语句执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 JET 3.5/3.51/4.0 版本，无需身份认证即可利用，可导致目标系统被完全控制。由于 Microsoft JET 引擎被广泛集成于多种应用程序中，攻击面较大，建议用户安装相应安全补丁或升级至更新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0325"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:28.873","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-030 提供的 Jet 数据库引擎更新补丁（下载地址：https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?FamilyID=3EFBE71A-00BB-48CE-930A-47FB9827E1E7），该补丁适用于 Jet 3.5 及后续版本。对于仍在使用 Jet 3.5 以下版本的系统，建议升级到 Jet 4.0 或更高版本。作为临时缓解措施，在 Office 中禁用 VBA 宏自动执行，不打开来源不明的 Access 数据库文件及包含数据库查询的 Office 文档。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/548","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-030","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3155","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19435","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0325.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0325.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0325","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0325.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0325.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m238-53hv-gp98/GHSA-m238-53hv-gp98.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0325.json","https://github.com/runZeroInc/divining-risk/blob/286d414a20238d70344afbbc3869527af7cea8e5/data/VulnCheck-KEV.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/548/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0271.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0271.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0271.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0809","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0809.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0323","title":"Microsoft Jet 数据库引擎 Text I-ISAM 组件文本文件修改漏洞","description":"Microsoft Jet 数据库引擎中的 Text I-ISAM 组件存在安全漏洞，攻击者可通过构造特制的数据库查询语句，利用该组件对目标系统上的文本文件进行非授权修改。该漏洞影响使用 Jet 数据库引擎的应用程序（如 Microsoft Access 等），攻击者无需高级权限即可触发，可能导致数据完整性受损。CVSS 评分 7.6，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0323"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:28.597","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Jet 数据库引擎安全更新 (MS99-030)，或升级至 Jet 4.0 Service Pack 5 及以上版本。如无法安装补丁，可通过限制对 Jet 数据库引擎的访问权限、禁用不必要的文本数据源 I-ISAM 驱动作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=1999-08-22&msg=19990729195531.25108.qmail%40underground.org","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-030","https://web.archive.org/web/20000819203059/http://xforce.iss.net:80/alerts/vol-4_num-7.php#jet-text-isam","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/595"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0809.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0908","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0908.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0353","title":"University of Washington Pine 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Pine 4.x 邮件客户端在处理 HTML 格式邮件时存在远程命令执行漏洞。当用户查看包含恶意链接的 HTML 邮件时，Pine 会调用 lynx 文本浏览器获取远程 Web 服务器上的 uuencoded 文件，随后自动解码并执行该文件，从而导致任意命令执行。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 Pine 4.x 所有版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0353"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:32.433","remediation":"升级到不再受影响的 Pine 5.0 以上版本，或迁移至其继任者 Alpine 邮件客户端。如无法升级，可在 Pine 配置中将 `url-viewers` 设置为空，禁用外部浏览器自动调用功能，并关闭 HTML 邮件自动渲染和 uudecode 自动解码特性以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/pine_update_announcement.html","http://www.novell.com/linux/security/advisories/suse_security_announce_6.html","http://www.securiteam.com/unixfocus/HHP-Pine_remote_exploit.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1247","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0353.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0353","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0353.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0353.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f37077e857e7a28bab83d284c23299407fb1af7e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-ccp8-f5cx-4p8g/GHSA-ccp8-f5cx-4p8g.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0353.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fbab718b-0c6e-49bf-a5f8-ce372a5cd908.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--fbab718b-0c6e-49bf-a5f8-ce372a5cd908.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0908.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0103","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0103.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0118","title":"RedHat Linux su 程序登录失败日志缺失导致密码暴力破解漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 系统中的 su 程序存在日志绕过漏洞。当 su 进程在超时前被强制终止时，系统不会记录失败的密码尝试日志，导致本地攻击者可以利用此缺陷进行暴力破解密码攻击，而不会在系统日志中留下痕迹。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 5.2 i386 及 6.0 版本，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级至修复版本或配置适当的日志审计机制。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0118"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-06-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:02.260","remediation":"升级至 Red Hat Linux 6.1 及以上版本，该版本已修复 su 程序在超时前被终止时不记录失败密码尝试的缺陷。如无法升级，可配置 syslog 的 authpriv 设施捕获所有认证事件，并部署 auditd 审计框架监控 su 执行行为作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94935300520617&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19255","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a662dc905cd549a2105daacbfce64cf01652761d/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0118.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0118","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0118.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0118.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pcr7-6q32-4xxw/GHSA-pcr7-6q32-4xxw.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/320/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0103.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0277","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0277.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0333","title":"Let me analyze this CVE: - CVE-2000-0333 - Affected products: tcpdump, Ethereal (Wireshark's former name) - Vulnerability type: DNS Decoder Infinite Loop - 拒绝服务漏洞 (Denial of Service) - The issue is in the DNS decoder that enters an infinite loop when processing malformed DNS packets The format should be: \"厂商 产品 漏洞类型\" For this vulnerability, the products are tcpdump and Ethereal. Let me craft a title that captures the vendor, product, and vulnerability type. The vendor would be the tcpdump group / Ethereal project, products are tcpdump and Ethereal, vulnerability type is 拒绝服务漏洞. Title: tcpdump/Ethereal DNS 解析器无限循环拒绝服务漏洞 Actually, let me think about this more carefully. The format is \"厂商 产品 漏洞类型\". - 厂商: Since tcpdump is from the tcpdump group and Ethereal was the predecessor to Wireshark, I could say \"tcpdump Group\" but that's not common. Typically we'd just say the product name as the vendor/product combination. - 产品: tcpdump/Ethereal - 漏洞类型: DNS 解析器无限循环拒绝服务漏洞","description":"tcpdump 和 Ethereal 等网络抓包工具的 DNS 解码器存在无限循环漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的畸形 DNS 数据包触发该漏洞。当数据包中的跳转偏移量指向自身时，tcpdump 在解压缩过程中会陷入无限循环，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 tcpdump 3.4/3.5 alpha 及 Ethereal 0.8.4/0.8.5/0.8.6 等版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，但需诱使目标用户或系统处理恶意构造的 DNS 流量。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0333"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:29.867","remediation":"升级 tcpdump 至 3.6 及以上版本，升级 Ethereal（现 Wireshark）至 0.8.7 及以上版本。现代系统应更新至 tcpdump 最新稳定版及 Wireshark 最新稳定版。如无法升级，可在抓包时使用过滤表达式 `not dns` 排除 DNS 流量，或禁用 DNS 解析器中的压缩指针解压功能作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1165","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.SOL.4.10.10005021942380.2077-100000%40paranoia.pgci.ca","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19892","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0333.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0333","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0333.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0333.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fpxw-v79p-g5g4/GHSA-fpxw-v79p-g5g4.json","https://github.com/tex2e/rfc-translater/blob/fe98548607fda36ec1bbbeb0817c0e6522d169e6/html/rfc9267.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0333.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0277.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0340","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0340.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0412","title":"John Donoghue Knapster/gnapster 客户端任意文件读取漏洞","description":"gnapster 和 knapster 是 Napster 网络的 P2P 客户端软件，其文件共享功能未对请求文件类型进行充分限制，仅默认允许 MP3 文件传输但未实际校验。远程攻击者可通过指定目标文件的绝对路径，绕过预期限制读取客户端系统上的任意文件（如密码文件、配置文件等），导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 John Donoghue Knapster 0.9 及 1.3.8 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0412"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:39.690","remediation":"立即停止使用 Knapster 客户端，该软件已停止维护且不再有安全更新。建议卸载 Knapster 并改用其他受支持的 Napster 兼容客户端（如 Napster 官方客户端）。如无法立即卸载，可在防火墙或路由器层面阻止该程序对外部 Napster 服务器的 6699/TCP 连接作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0124.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0127.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1186","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19905","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0412.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0412","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0412.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0412.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-jvph-5pfg-9gfc/GHSA-jvph-5pfg-9gfc.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/gnapster_get_file.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0412.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0340.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0137","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0137.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0153","title":"Microsoft Personal Web Server 远程目录遍历漏洞","description":"Microsoft Personal Web Server (PWS) 存在远程目录遍历漏洞，属于路径穿越类安全缺陷。攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含多个 \"..\"（点点）序列的特制 HTTP 请求，即可突破路径限制，读取服务器上任意可读文件，包括系统配置文件、源代码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Personal Web Server 多个版本，危害等级中等，微软已在 MS99-010 安全公告中发布修复补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0153"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:06.647","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-010 提供的补丁程序，或升级至 Internet Information Server (IIS) 4.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在 Web 服务器配置中禁用父路径（Parent Paths）功能，并限制网站根目录外的文件访问权限。由于 Personal Web Server 已停止支持，建议迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/989","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=000801bf780a%249ad4b2e0%240100007f%40localhost","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0153.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0153","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0153.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0153.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vvx9-rq2w-m3vg/GHSA-vvx9-rq2w-m3vg.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0153.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/989/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/27329332eaf6d7802a105e6a6dc78246a75b7339/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0137.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0017","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0017.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0019","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16251,\"outputTokens\":36,\"totalTokens\":16287}}","description":"IMail POP3 守护进程使用了强度不足的加密机制来保护用户邮件数据。攻击者若已获取目标系统的本地访问权限，可利用该加密缺陷解密并读取其他用户的 POP3 邮件文件内容，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响运行 IMail Server 的 Windows 系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级较低。由于需要本地访问权限，攻击条件较为严格，仅本地恶意用户或已入侵系统的攻击者可利用此弱点获取邮件隐私数据。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0019"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-03-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:50.127","remediation":"升级 Ipswitch IMail 至 5.0 或更高版本，该版本修复了 POP3 守护进程使用弱加密存储密码的问题。如无法升级，在服务器本地限制非授权用户登录，避免本地低权限用户通过读取 POP3 密码文件获取其他用户邮箱访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0019","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/2000/CVE-2000-0019.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fb6d88d74424546f8735bb570a195f07b71e3801/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0019.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0019","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/0377100217e5863bf7971fe361bbd36f2839fecf/2000/CVE-2000-0019.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0019.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e28f1b2cbe9256d47132558d422c401a0de0ac99/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0019.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88240/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/3bce2247ecd36c1e0bf5c43dc6ed72018b618696/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0017.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0154","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0154.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0054","title":"SolutionScripts Home Free 1.0 search.cgi 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Solution Scripts Home Free 1.0 的 search.cgi 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 URL 参数中注入 `../` 序列绕过路径限制，读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入的路径参数进行充分过滤，导致攻击者可遍历目录结构，泄露敏感配置文件或系统信息。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0054"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:54.393","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，建议立即删除或禁用 search.cgi 脚本，或迁移至其他仍在维护的论坛/留言板系统。如必须继续使用，应在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）层面配置 URL 重写规则，过滤 `../` 等目录遍历字符，并限制脚本对文件系统的访问权限。同时建议升级至 PHP/Node.js 等现代语言编写的替代方案，避免使用已停止维护的 CGI 脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/921","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19713","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d25d3aeab9dc76030f155f9e202a4a7c294f86bf/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0054.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0054","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0054.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0054.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xmgh-66hw-7378/GHSA-xmgh-66hw-7378.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0054.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/921/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/homefree.nasl","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0154.toml"}]